    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Growth
---
All spiritual growth takes place as a gradual harmonious unfolding. It
happens automatically. As you live up to your highest light, acting on your
inspirations, more and more light comes to you. There is no hurry or
impatience to get anything; it comes as you are ready.
